How to Compile (Windows/Linux)
	qmake && make

How to Compile (Mac)
	qmake -spec macx-g++ && make

How to Run Example (Linux)
	cd example
	qmake && make
	sh unix-run.sh

How to Run Example (Mac)
	copy 'bin/MacNavBar.framework' to '/Library/Frameworks'
	cd example
	qmake -spec macx-g++ && make
	open example.app

